REMARK 400 COMPOUND                                                             
REMARK 400 VANCOMYCIN IS A TRICYCLIC GLYCOPEPTIDE. THE SCAFFOLD IS A            
REMARK 400 HEPTAPEPTIDE WITH THE CONFIGURATION D-D-L-D-D-L-L. IT IS FURTHER     
REMARK 400 GLYCOSYLATED BY A DISACCHARIDE MADE OF D-GLUCOSE AND VANCOSAMINE.    
REMARK 400 HERE, VANCOMYCIN IS REPRESENTED BY GROUPING TOUGHER THE SEQUENCE     
REMARK 400 (SEQRES) AND THE TWO LIGANDS (HET) BGC AND RER.                      
